<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="card border border-secondary-subtle shadow-sm my-5">
    <div class="card-header bg-transparent border-0 pt-5 pb-0 text-center">
      <h2 class="h4 fw-bold">ABOUT</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body px-4 pb-5 text-center">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-xl" style="color: #8E44AD;"></i>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-xl" style="color: #2ECC71;"></i>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-xl" style="color: #3498DB;"></i>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle fa-xl" style="color: #F1C40F"></i>
      </div>
      <p class="fs-5 text-dark mb-2">
        「自分を知り、世界を広げる。16タイプで紐解く新しい繋がり。」
      </p>
      <p class="text-secondary small">
        他では通じなかったあなたの本音、ここで話してみませんか？
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark text-secondary me-2"></i>
        <h4 class="h5 fw-bold mb-0">New Posts</h4>
      </div>

      <div class="border-top border-secondary-subtle">
        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
          <div class="py-3 border-bottom">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center flex-grow-1">
                <div class="text-muted small me-3" style="min-width: 50px;">
                  <%= post.updated_at.strftime("%m/%d") %>
                </div>
                
                <div class="me-3">
                  <%= render 'shared/mbti_badge', type: post.user.mbti_type %>
                </div>

                <div class="fw-bold">
                  <%= link_to post.title, post_path(post), class: "text-dark text-decoration-none" %>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <%= link_to "詳細へ", post_path(post), class: "btn btn-link btn-sm text-secondary p-0 text-decoration-none fw-bold" %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-5 mb-5">
        <%= link_to "すべての投稿を見る", posts_path, class: "btn btn-outline-dark px-5" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>